<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今後的關係會越來越親密喔。<10_4 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就像<delay20 />最好的朋友那種感覺<tag a="110" b="0" />？<pageBreak /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵呵，雖然突然這麼跟你說，<delay20 />
