<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過，今後也請你多多關照囉，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="201" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
